=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_FBSineL_ex6 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright mixed sound, with complex oscillator character around 51 Hz, featuring moderate attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: moderate
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 50.8740
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0481
  harmonic_regularity: 0.2027
  pitch_clarity: 21.8605
  inharmonicity: 0.0407
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -27.1771
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

